      "Hello there! We are an application that connects local small businesses with aspiring app developers! How can we
      help you
      today?"
   </h3>
   <div id="find-help" class="who col-md-6">
      <h2 class="subtitle">Find a Raccoon</h2>
      <div class="row post-job">
         <button class="main-button" id="post-job-btn">postJob</button>
      </div>
      <div class="row find-raccoon">
         <button class="main-button" id="find-raccoon-btn">findRaccoon</button>
